<div class="mktEditable" id="WorcesterContent" ><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="700" align="center" bgcolor="#ffffff">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 33px; padding-right: 33px;" width="634">
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><a href="http://www.solar4worcester.com"><img src="http://pages.astrumsolar.com/rs/astrumsolarinc/images/AstrumSolar_Worcester_Header_SpreadTheWord.jpg" border="0" alt="Spread the word in Massachusetts and get rewarded" width="634" height="340" /></a></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 33px; padding-right: 33px;" width="634">
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom-color: #cccccc; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px;">
<p style="color: #016b9d; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 25px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">Did You Know You Can Earn Cash for Referrals?</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">Astrum Solar is spreading the word about solar to Massachusetts residents! Astrum Solar&rsquo;s business is based on the numerous referrals from our satisfied customers. A 9.8 kW solar home is at the root of the Astrum Solar customer family tree that got its start in one community.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 35px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">We love referrals and reward our customers who spread the word about the benefits of going solar the right way with Astrum Solar. Do you know someone in Massachusetts who may benefit from going solar? As an Astrum Solar customer, you can earn a cash reward for any referral that switches to solar with Astrum Solar&mdash;you will receive $250 and your referral will receive $250!*</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 33px; padding-right: 33px;" width="634">
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom-color: #cccccc; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px;">
<p style="color: #016b9d; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">$1,000 Discount for Massachusetts Residents!</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 35px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">When you refer your friends and family to Astrum Solar, they will enjoy their independence from unpredictable electricity prices and lock in their own electricity rates. Choosing solar will put them in control of their own power generation and free them from ever-increasing utility rates. <strong>In addition to these benefits, they&rsquo;ll receive a $1,000 discount through September 30!**</strong> Encourage your friends and family friends and family to request their free roof surveys today to take advantage of this special offer!</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 33px; padding-right: 33px;" width="634">
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom-color: #cccccc; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 1px;">
<p style="color: #016b9d; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 24px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">Referring is as Easy as 1-2-3!</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: bold; color: #016b9d;">1.)</span> Encourage your friends and family to visit <a style="color: #0097c9; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.solar4worcester.com">www.solar4worcester.com</a></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: bold; color: #016b9d;">2.)</span> When your referral fills out the form and reaches the &ldquo;How did you hear about us&rdquo; field, they should select &ldquo;Referral by Customer/Employee.&rdquo;</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 35px; margin-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-weight: bold; color: #016b9d;">3.)</span> A text box will populate. Your referral should include your name as the referring party. That&rsquo;s it!</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 33px; padding-right: 33px;" width="634">
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
<p style="color: #016b9d; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 32px; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;"><span class="appleLinksDarkBlue">Special Event on August 26</span></p>
<p style="color: #016b9d; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 26px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 5px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;"><span class="appleLinksDarkBlue">7:00 PM &ndash; 8:00 PM</span></p>
<p style="color: #016b9d; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; font-weight: bold;"><span class="appleLinksDarkBlue">Courtyard Worcester &nbsp;|&nbsp; 72 Grove Street &nbsp;|&nbsp; Worcester, MA 01605</span></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">Astrum Solar will be hosting a Solar Seminar <span class="appleLinksGray">on August 26</span> for all Massachusetts residents, families, and friends! Join us for a short presentation and learn about the money-saving and environmental benefits of going solar with Astrum. Refreshments will be served.</p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; padding-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">An expert will be on hand to answer any questions about what&rsquo;s involved in going solar and to assess solar potential and electricity savings for Massachusetts residents. This is a great opportunity for your friends and family in Massachusetts to learn about the benefits of going solar, and for you to get rewarded for referring them. Encourage them to reserve their spot at this special event!</p>
<div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 40px;"><a href="http://solarforworcester.eventbrite.com"><img src="http://pages.astrumsolar.com/rs/astrumsolarinc/images/AstrumSolar_Worcester_SpreadWordButton.jpg" border="0" alt="View event information and spread the word!!" width="500" height="45" /></a></div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
