<div class="mktEditable" id="WorcesterCopyPromoDetails" ><p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><span class="appleLinksGray">*You must be an Astrum Solar customer to participate in the Astrum Solar Referral Program. For each referral that signs a solar contract with Astrum Solar, you will receive $250 and your referral will receive $250. Individuals may not refer themselves. Referrals must have no prior contact with Astrum Solar to be considered a customer referral. Payment is sent within 30 days of the sale.</span></p>
<p style="color: #666666; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0px;"><span class="appleLinksGray">**LIMITED TIME OFFER: Valid for qualifying homes that sign a new solar system contract with Astrum Solar by September 30, 2014. In lieu of a cash rebate, customers can opt to use the $1,000 as a down payment to reduce their monthly solar fees or to receive a $1,000 discount off the contract price at the time of their purchase. Otherwise, $1,000 cash back rebate to be mailed approximately 30 days after the system is installed. Minimum system size is 5 kW. Qualifying homes must be located in a territory that Astrum Solar serves. Offer is in addition to other available promotions or discounts.</span></p></div>
